      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>透過物質文化、環境及動物遺骸的遺跡研究人類歷史。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
